column3: Closed because it's not really a pull request!
Better topic for bitcoin-dev. There are (as far as I know, yet) no proposals for a flexible blocksize which actually acheive their goals, and its not because people havent tried.

For future reference, you can generate such a comparison without a dummy-PR as follows:\n["https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/compare/master...BitcoinUnlimited:release"](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/compare/master...BitcoinUnlimited:release)
